 According to an eye witness at the scene, a pregnant woman was wounded and a client refueling his vehicle was shot in the head during the shootout. Emergency response personnel battled to stabilise the man at the scene before rushing him to hospital.  Some of the suspects fled in a brown VW Polo, while the other suspects fled on foot. An eye witness reports that the shooters had disappeared before police arrived. The condition of the victims remains unknown at this time.      One dead in early morning crash Fake notes in Belfast leads to two arrests Theft of motor vehicles on the rise Accident claims the life of an infant • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za  